name: MyTacoChef
0:
”Alexa, ask My Taco Chef for a taco”
”Alexa, tell My Taco Chef to give me a recipe”
”Alexa, open My Taco Chef”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my taco chef
des:
My Taco Chef is a simple, yet powerful skill that brings a variety of Tacos and Taco recipes right to your home. 

You'll always get something new!
My Taco Chef pulls from a public collection of user-submitted taco recipes, so you'll always find a new and interesting recipe. 

Icon made by Madebyoliver from www.flaticon.com
For the best experience, have your Alexa App nearby to get the full recipe.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
